data.description: Vista Del Sol, perfect 55+ Community in Sunny St. George. HOA is $242 a month and includes clubhouse, tennis courts, indoor pool, exterior building insurance, water and full yard maintenance. This home was built in 1994, 1,687sqft, 3bd, 2ba, 2cg. Newly updated with all brand new Frigidaire stainless steel appliances (microwave, stove, dishwasher, refrigerator), new washer and dryer, new carpet, repainted kitchen cabinets, new water heater and expansion tank, and new AC/Furnace in 2022. Home includes a newly installed Vivint security system. A back patio automated sun screen. Nuvo H2O water softener and filtration system. Granite kitchen counter tops with pantry. This is the perfect primary. secondary, or investment property. Updates already completed. Furniture is available for sale.
